---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Commercial Carpet Cleaning Services | Montreal & Laval"
  description="Professional commercial carpet cleaning for offices and businesses. Competitive rates, flexible hours, and superior results. Free estimate."
>
  <!-- SPLIT SCREEN HERO -->
  <div class="split-hero-container">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: CONTENT (Hook) -->
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">COMMERCIAL</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Commercial Carpet Cleaning
          </h1>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100">
            <h3 class="problem-title">The Problem:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              Your company's image starts with cleanliness. Stained or dusty carpets harm your reputation and the air quality of your offices.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            A professional maintenance service designed for your business spaces. Flexible plans, fast drying, and impeccable results for offices and retail stores.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-gradient-green pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Talk to an Expert)
            </a>
            <button
              onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()"
              class="btn btn-gradient-green"
            >
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Instant Online Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: IMAGE (Visual / Slideshow) -->
        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-14.webp"
              alt="Commercial office carpet cleaning Montreal - Empire Group"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-18.webp"
              alt="Commercial building corridor carpet maintenance Laval"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-19.webp"
              alt="Conference room carpet cleaning South Shore"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-30.webp"
              alt="Fast drying commercial carpet truck-mount Longueuil"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-31.webp"
              alt="Impeccable store entrance carpet Montreal - Professional result"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container alternate-layout">
      <div class="service-main-content">
        
        <div class="info-block">
          <h2 class="text-gradient-empire">Commercial Expertise and Large Spaces</h2>
          <p>The appearance of your professional premises—from majestic lobbies to reception rooms—is the first impression you give to your clients and employees. At <strong>Empire Cleaning Group</strong>, we understand that carpets stained or encrusted with winter calcium (salt) harm your reputation.</p>
          <p>Our specialized service for businesses in <strong>Montreal</strong>, <strong>Laval</strong>, and the <strong>South Shore</strong> guarantees high-performance cleaning for all types of traffic, without ever interrupting your opening hours thanks to our flexible scheduling (evenings and weekends).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Solutions adapted for every industry</h3>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li><strong>Office buildings:</strong> Cubicles, conference rooms, and common areas.</li>
            <li><strong>Retail stores:</strong> High-traffic entrance mats (salt/calcium removal).</li>
            <li><strong>Hospitality and restaurants:</strong> Printed commercial carpets, corridors, and accent chairs.</li>
            <li><strong>Daycare Centers (CPEs):</strong> Disinfection without harsh chemicals (safe for babies).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 5-STEP PROCESS -->
        <div class="process-section" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
          <h2 class="text-gradient-empire">Our Commercial Protocol (5 Steps)</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">We do not use the "bonnet" method (surface friction) which pushes dirt downwards. We use hot water extraction (high-temperature steam) for deep sanitation.</p>
          <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Logistical Inspection & Quote</h3>
                <p>Analysis of high-traffic areas (main corridors), types of stains (coffee, ink, salt), and planning of the intervention outside opening hours for zero interruption.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Anti-Calcium & Degreasing Treatment</h3>
                <p>Application of a specific industrial pre-treatment that dissolves salt crusts, urea, and body grease accumulations in the carpet fibers.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Vacuuming and Mechanical Brushing</h3>
                <p>Agitation of fibers with counter-rotating brushes to lift the crushed pile of the commercial carpet and dislodge encysted dirt at the base.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>High-Power Steam Extraction</h3>
                <p>Use of our highest-end equipment (powerful truck-mount or commercial portable for office towers) to rinse and extract 95% of the moisture.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">5</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Accelerated Drying & Report</h3>
                <p>Placement of axial fans (air movers) if necessary to ensure the premises are dry and ready for use the next morning. Delivery of a certified service report.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BENEFITS -->
        <div class="fade-in-section delay-200" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
          <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
            Why choose Empire Group in B2B?
          </h2>
          <div class="benefits-grid">
            <div class="benefit-item">
              <div class="check-circle">✓</div>
              <span><strong>Flexible hours:</strong> Evening, night, or weekend interventions with no hidden fees.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
              <div class="check-circle">✓</div>
              <span><strong>Liability insurance:</strong> Comprehensive $2M coverage for your peace of mind in a corporate environment.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
              <div class="check-circle">✓</div>
              <span><strong>Certified technicians:</strong> Uniformed, discreet, professional, and vetted staff (Background check).</span>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
              <div class="check-circle">✓</div>
              <span><strong>Very fast drying:</strong> Thanks to our superior extraction, your premises are usable in a few hours.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
              <div class="check-circle">✓</div>
              <span><strong>Multi-site capability:</strong> We can service multiple branches across the greater metropolitan area.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SERVICED ZONES -->
        <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">Service Perimeter — Commercial Sector</h3>
          <p>We cover all business hubs in the greater metropolitan area with dedicated commercial units.</p>

          <div class="city-group">
            <p class="city-lead">🏙️ Montreal (Business Hubs)</p>
            <div class="badges-container">
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Downtown (Office Towers)</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Old Montreal</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Anjou Industrial Park</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Saint-Laurent Technoparc</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Pointe-Claire & West Island</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="city-group">
            <p class="city-lead">🏘️ Laval & North Shore</p>
            <div class="badges-container">
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Centropolis & Chomedey</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Centre Industrial Park</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Sainte-Rose (Retail)</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="city-group">
            <p class="city-lead">🌿 Montreal South Shore</p>
            <div class="badges-container">
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Quartier DIX30 (Brossard)</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Longueuil Industrial Park</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Boucherville (Eiffel Sector)</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Saint-Bruno-de-Montarville</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ with Schema Component -->
        <FAQSchema
          title="Frequently Asked Questions — Commercial Service"
          faqs={[
              {
                question: "What is the best cleaning method for high-traffic commercial carpets?",
                answer: "Hot water extraction steam cleaning is the most effective method for commercial carpets (deep restoration). Unlike encapsulation or bonnet cleaning (buffing) which only clean the surface and trap dirt, our extraction method deeply removes salt, winter calcium, and accumulated body oils. This extends the carpet's lifespan and prevents premature crushing of the fibers."
              },
              {
                question: "How long do I have to close my offices after a professional carpet cleaning?",
                answer: "Zero hours of closure. We work outside your peak hours (evenings or weekends) to minimize business interruptions. Thanks to our very high-suction equipment, commercial carpets (which are very short-piled) usually dry in 2 to 4 hours. By the next morning, your premises are completely dry, fresh, and ready for regular traffic."
              },
              {
                question: "Do I need to move office furniture before you arrive?",
                answer: "No, we handle the majority of the logistics. We simply ask you to clear the floor (boxes, papers) and move small trash cans or rolling chairs from the areas to be cleaned. We clean professionally around cubicles, heavy desks, and bookcases without moving them to avoid any breakage or IT disconnection (servers/cables)."
              },
              {
                question: "Do you offer annual preventive maintenance contracts?",
                answer: "Absolutely. Waiting until the carpet is visibly dirty is often too late. We offer scheduled maintenance plans (quarterly or semi-annually) for high-traffic corridors and annually for closed offices. Preventive contracts guarantee a locked-in rate and technically extend the life of your flooring by 3 to 5 years."
              },
              {
                question: "How do you remove hard white crusts of calcium (salt) at my store entrance?",
                answer: "Calcium (sodium chloride) is highly alkaline and burns commercial fibers if left untreated. We apply a specific professional neutralizer that chemically dissolves hardened salt crystals without damaging the carpet. We then proceed with a massive hot water extraction. This is a must-do treatment in Quebec during the spring."
              },
              {
                question: "Can you clean our office chairs or our cubicle partitions?",
                answer: "Yes, our commercial service is comprehensive. We clean over 500 ergonomic chairs and fabric partition panels (cubicles) every year. We use specialized manual extraction tools that remove coffee stains, printer toner, and body sebum without staining the metal or plastic components of the chairs."
              }
            ]}
          />
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  // Simple Cross-Fade Slideshow
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");

  if (slides.length > 0) {
    let currentSlide = 0;
    const intervalTime = 4000; // 4 seconds

    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, intervalTime);
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  /* SPLIT SCREEN HERO (Sky Blue Theme) */
  .split-hero-container {
    background-color: #fff;
    padding-top: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100vw;
  }

  .full-width-split {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .split-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: stretch;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  /* LEFT TEXT COLUMN */
  .split-content {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .service-cat-badge {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .split-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .problem-statement {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-left: 4px solid #ff4444;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3);
  }

  .problem-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #cc0000;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .problem-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 650px;
  }

  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cta-group {
      display: none !important;
    }
  }

  .split-content .btn-secondary-outline {
    border-color: #ddd;
    color: #666;
  }
  .split-content .btn-secondary-outline:hover {
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* RIGHT IMAGE COLUMN */
  .split-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 500px;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 0;
    transform: none;
    box-shadow: none;
    margin: 0;
    background-color: #fff;
  }

  .slideshow-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }

  .slide.active {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .split-content {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      order: 1;
    }

    .split-image-wrapper {
      order: 2;
      height: 400px;
      min-height: 0;
    }

    .lead-text {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* LAYOUT */
  .service-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
  }

  /* TYPOGRAPHY */
  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-text-reveal {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-text-reveal:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .seo-content-hidden {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
  }

  .seo-content-hidden.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  .separator {
    border: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .seo-content-hidden p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
  }

  .seo-content-hidden strong {
    color: var(--color-empire-red);
  }

  .seo-content-hidden ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .seo-content-hidden li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* NEW SECTIONS CSS */
  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .benefit-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
    background: white;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .check-circle {
    width: 25px;
    height: 25px;
    background: #e6f7e6;
    color: #2e7d32;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .faq-list {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .question {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .answer {
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* NEW COMMERCIAL CSS CLASSES */
  .alternate-layout { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  .info-block { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); }
  .check-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .check-list li { padding: 0.5rem 0; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative; }
  .check-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: bold; position: absolute; left: 0; }
  
  .process-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; position: relative; }
  .process-steps::before { content: ""; position: absolute; left: 20px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: #eee; z-index: 0; }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; position: relative; z-index: 1; align-items: flex-start; }
  .step-num { flex-shrink: 0; width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-primary); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; border: 4px solid white; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .step-text h3 { color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .step-text p { color: #555; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  
  .zones-section { padding: 2rem; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #eaeaea; }
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .city-lead { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: #444; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
  .badge { padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; color: #004a9f; border: 1px solid #c5dff0; }
  .badge-green { background: #e9f5e9; color: #2e7d32; border: 1px solid #c8e6c9; }
</style>
